### ForTheWeebs API Testing
### Use the REST Client extension (humao.rest-client) to run these tests
### Instructions: Click "Send Request" above each request to execute

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================

### Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "displayName": "Test User"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### ============================================
### POSTS
### ============================================

### Get Feed
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/feed?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This is a test post from VS Code!",
  "mediaUrls": ["https://example.com/image.jpg"],
  "visibility": "public"
}

### Get Single Post
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/POST_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Like Post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/POST_ID_HERE/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Share Post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/POST_ID_HERE/share
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete Post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/POST_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### COMMENTS
### ============================================

### Get Comments for Post
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/post/POST_ID_HERE?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Comment
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": "POST_ID_HERE",
  "content": "Great post!",
  "parentCommentId": null
}

### Like Comment
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments/COMMENT_ID_HERE/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete Comment
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/comments/COMMENT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### RELATIONSHIPS
### ============================================

### Follow User
POST {{baseUrl}}/relationships/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "USER_ID_HERE"
}

### Unfollow User
POST {{baseUrl}}/relationships/unfollow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "USER_ID_HERE"
}

### Get Followers
GET {{baseUrl}}/relationships/followers/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Following
GET {{baseUrl}}/relationships/following/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send Friend Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/relationships/friend-request
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "USER_ID_HERE"
}

### Accept Friend Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/relationships/friend-accept
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "USER_ID_HERE"
}

### Block User
POST {{baseUrl}}/relationships/block
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "USER_ID_HERE"
}

### ============================================
### MESSAGES
### ============================================

### Get Conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Messages in Conversation
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversation/CONVERSATION_ID_HERE?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/send
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientId": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "body": "Hey! How are you?",
  "mediaUrls": []
}

### Mark Message as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/MESSAGE_ID_HERE/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Unread Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### NOTIFICATIONS
### ============================================

### Get Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Unread Notification Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark Notification as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/NOTIFICATION_ID_HERE/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark All Notifications as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/mark-all-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete Notification
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notifications/NOTIFICATION_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### SUBSCRIPTIONS
### ============================================

### Get My Subscriptions
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/my-subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get My Subscribers
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/my-subscribers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Checkout Session
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "creatorId": "CREATOR_ID_HERE",
  "tier": "basic"
}

### Check Subscription Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/status/CREATOR_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/SUBSCRIPTION_ID_HERE/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
